      <para id="id1170650406501">Amazing buildings: summaries</para>
      <para id="id1170656655528">Remember to answer the questions <emphasis effect="bold">WHAT</emphasis><emphasis effect="bold">?</emphasis><emphasis effect="bold">WHERE</emphasis><emphasis effect="bold">?</emphasis><emphasis effect="bold">WHO</emphasis><emphasis effect="bold">?</emphasis><emphasis effect="bold">WHY?</emphasis> and <emphasis effect="bold">AMAZING?</emphasis></para>
